OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment closes in on    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fenergy rescue plan         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Help for consumers' energy costs is to 
OL,6, be provided by allowing energy         
OL,7, suppliers to take out government-backed
OL,8, loans in order to subsidise bills.     
OL,10,FThe plan, which had been suggested by  
OL,11,Fthe energy industry, is set to be      
OL,12,Fannounced on Thursday.                 
OL,14,FThe "deficit reduction scheme" is      
OL,15,Fexpected to form the centre piece of   
OL,16,Fthe government's attempt to tackle the 
OL,17,Fhigh cost of energy for consumers.     
OL,19,FSmall business are also expected to be 
OL,20,Foffered some relief.                   
